name: TrulyAnything
description:
Can the (in)famous anything series generate literally anything? No. They can't generate anything apart from anime styles.

So here you go. An ambitious model that can generate literally anything; from anime style to photorealistic "atashi".

The model was trained based on ChaosMix, with images generated from MoeSharpV1 and "atashi" the artificial girlfriend.

It is NAI leak free, and yet powerful because the basic model is the latest Stable Diffusion 2.1 768.

I didn't upload a yaml because it's no longer necessary when using webUI. If you need one, just download and rename it from somewhere.

Sample images will be added later.
